(246, 23, 0, 'dasd', '<p><span>Sendo p(x) = ax4 + bx³ + c e q(x) = ax³ – bx – c, determine os coeficientes a, b e c, sabendo que p(0) = 0, p(1) = 0 e q(1) = 2.</span></p>', 1, '<p>p(0) = 0 → a * 04 + b * 03 + c = 0 → c = 0</p>\n<p>p(1) = 0 → a * 14 + b * 13 + 0 = 0 → a + b = 0</p>\n<p>q(1) = 2 → a * 13 – b * 1 – 0 = 2 → a – b = 2</p>\n<p><img src="http://www.brasilescola.com/upload/conteudo/images/Untitled-41.gif" alt="" /></p>\n<p>Temos que a = 1, b = – 1 e c = 0</p>', 1, 1.0000000, 0.3333333, 'match', 1, 'moodle.ufsc.br+140613073404+BlVURv', 'moodle.ufsc.br+140613073404+L9adbN', 0, 1402644844, 1402644844, 2, 2),
